reviews.text: Food selection is good, but needs to provide more solutions for coffee. Such as to provide fresh cream, half&half, almond milk, soya milk.... Etc.
The staff here are always so lovely and see to care about you with personality. The panini's are tasty. Rest of the food not so much.
Sun is a great barister and manager ....very friendly
Their coffee is slightly better than neighboring Starbucks. Good seating. At times can get busy, but other than that, cosy and quiet.
A convenient place to recharge.
